[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 3 [39m[48;5;95m ## Overview[49m                                                                                                     [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 4 [39m[48;5;95m Artifish is a project for creating autonomous AI agents that interact with th[49m                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95me Bluesky social network. These agents, collectively known as "Artifish," oper[49m                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95mate through a custom PDS (Personal Data Server) hosted at art.ifi.sh.[49m                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 3 [39m[48;5;65m This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.[49m          [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;65m code in this repository.[49m                                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 4 [39m                                                                                                                 [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 5 [39m[48;5;95m ## Core Components[49m                                                                                              [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 5 [39m[48;5;65m ## Commands[49m                                                                                                     [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 6 [39m[48;5;65m - Setup: `./setup.sh` to create venv and install dependencies[49m                                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 7 [39m[48;5;65m - Run: `python -m artifish.agent` to run the main agent[49m                                                         [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 8 [39m[48;5;65m - Tests: `pytest` or `pytest tests/specific_test.py` for single test[49m                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 9 [39m[48;5;65m - Format: `black .` for code formatting[49m                                                                         [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m10 [39m[48;5;65m - Type check: `mypy artifish/`[49m                                                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m11 [39m                                                                                                                 [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m12 [39m[48;5;95m 1. **Agent System**[49m                                                                                             [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m13 [39m[48;5;95m    - Built using Google's Agent Development Kit (ADK)[49m                                                           [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m14 [39m[48;5;95m    - Hierarchical structure with Boss-C as the orchestrator agent[49m                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m15 [39m[48;5;95m    - Multiple specialized agents that perform different functions[49m                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m12 [39m[48;5;65m ## Coding Guidelines[49m                                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m13 [39m[48;5;65m - **Style**: PEP 8 compliant, 4-space indentation[49m                                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m14 [39m[48;5;65m - **Imports**: stdlib first, third-party next, local imports last[49m                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m15 [39m[48;5;65m - **Type Hints**: Required for all function parameters and returns[49m                                              [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m16 [39m[48;5;65m - **Docstrings**: Google style with Args/Returns sections[49m                                                       [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m17 [39m[48;5;65m - **Error Handling**: Use try/except with specific exceptions and logging[49m                                       [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m18 [39m[48;5;65m - **Naming**: [49m                                                                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m19 [39m[48;5;65m   - Classes: CamelCase[49m                                                                                          [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m20 [39m[48;5;65m   - Functions/variables: snake_case[49m                                                                             [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m21 [39m[48;5;65m   - Private methods: _prefixed[49m                                                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m22 [39m[48;5;65m - **Architecture**: Modular with clear separation of concerns[49m                                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m23 [39m                                                                                                                 [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m24 [39m[48;5;95m 2. **Database Layer**[49m                                                                                           [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m25 [39m[48;5;95m    - Supabase for persistent storage[49m                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m26 [39m[48;5;95m    - Tables for artifish, bluesky_accounts, humans, post_references, post_con[49m                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95mtent, etc.[49m                                                                                                       [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m27 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memory system for storing persistent information about users and interac[49m                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95mtions[49m                                                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m28 [39m[48;5;95m [49m                                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m29 [39m[48;5;95m 3. **Memory System**[49m                                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m30 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memgraph for graph-based memory and relationship modeling[49m                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m31 [39m[48;5;95m    - Emojikeys for sentiment analysis[49m                                                                           [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m32 [39m[48;5;95m    - Interest tracking for understanding users' preferences[49m                                                     [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m33 [39m[48;5;95m [49m                                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m34 [39m[48;5;95m 4. **Network Crawler**[49m                                                                                          [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m35 [39m[48;5;95m    - Utility to explore and map the Bluesky social graph[49m                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m36 [39m[48;5;95m    - Collects relationships and interest data for agents[49m                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m37 [39m[48;5;95m [49m                                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m38 [39m[48;5;95m ## Key Libraries[49m                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m39 [39m[48;5;95m - Google ADK (Agent Development Kit) for agent orchestration[49m                                                    [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m27 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memory system for storing persistent information about users and interactions[49m                              [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 4 [39m[48;5;95m Artifish is a project for creating autonomous AI agents that interact with the Bluesky social network. These a[49m  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95mgents, collectively known as "Artifish," operate through a custom PDS (Personal Data Server) hosted at art.ifi.[49m  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 3 [39m[48;5;65m This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.[49m          [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 4 [39m                                                                                                                 [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 5 [39m[48;5;65m ## Commands[49m                                                                                                     [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m 6 [39m[48;5;65m - Setup: `./setup.sh` to create venv and install dependencies[49m                                                   [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m12 [39m[48;5;65m ## Coding Guidelines[49m                                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m13 [39m[48;5;65m - **Style**: PEP 8 compliant, 4-space indentation[49m                                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m14 [39m[48;5;65m - **Imports**: stdlib first, third-party next, local imports last[49m                                               [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m15 [39m[48;5;65m - **Type Hints**: Required for all function parameters and returns[49m                                              [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m16 [39m[48;5;65m - **Docstrings**: Google style with Args/Returns sections[49m                                                       [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m17 [39m[48;5;65m - **Error Handling**: Use try/except with specific exceptions and logging[49m                                       [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m18 [39m[48;5;65m - **Naming**: [49m                                                                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m25 [39m[48;5;95m    - Supabase for persistent storage[49m                                                                            [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m26 [39m[48;5;95m    - Tables for artifish, bluesky_accounts, humans, post_references, post_content, etc.[49m                         [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m27 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memory system for storing persistent information about users and interactions[49m                              [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m
[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m28 [39m[48;5;95m [49m                                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m30 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memgraph for graph-based memory and relationship modeling[49m                                                  [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m33 [39m[48;5;95m [49m                                                                                                                [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

[38;5;153m│[39m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;246m25 [39m[48;5;65m Artifish is a suite of AI agents for Bluesky built with Google ADK, using Supabase for storage and Memgraph for[49m [38;5;244m│[39m [38;5;153m│[39m

     [38;5;246m 4 [39m[48;5;95m Artifish is a project for creating autonomous AI agents that interact with the Bluesky social network. These[49m
     [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95m agents, collectively known as "Artifish," operate through a custom PDS (Personal Data Server) hosted at art.[49m
     [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;95mifi.sh.[49m
     [38;5;246m 3 [39m[48;5;65m This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.[49m
     [38;5;246m 4 [39m
     [38;5;246m 5 [39m[48;5;95m ## Core Components[49m
     [38;5;246m 5 [39m[48;5;65m ## Commands[49m
     [38;5;246m 6 [39m[48;5;65m - Setup: `./setup.sh` to create venv and install dependencies[49m
     [38;5;246m 7 [39m[48;5;65m - Run: `python -m artifish.agent` to run the main agent[49m
     [38;5;246m 8 [39m[48;5;65m - Tests: `pytest` or `pytest tests/specific_test.py` for single test[49m
     [38;5;246m 9 [39m[48;5;65m - Format: `black .` for code formatting[49m
     [38;5;246m10 [39m[48;5;65m - Type check: `mypy artifish/`[49m
     [38;5;246m11 [39m
     [38;5;246m12 [39m[48;5;95m 1. **Agent System**[49m
     [38;5;246m13 [39m[48;5;95m    - Built using Google's Agent Development Kit (ADK)[49m
     [38;5;246m14 [39m[48;5;95m    - Hierarchical structure with Boss-C as the orchestrator agent[49m
     [38;5;246m15 [39m[48;5;95m    - Multiple specialized agents that perform different functions[49m
     [38;5;246m12 [39m[48;5;65m ## Coding Guidelines[49m
     [38;5;246m13 [39m[48;5;65m - **Style**: PEP 8 compliant, 4-space indentation[49m
     [38;5;246m14 [39m[48;5;65m - **Imports**: stdlib first, third-party next, local imports last[49m
     [38;5;246m15 [39m[48;5;65m - **Type Hints**: Required for all function parameters and returns[49m
     [38;5;246m16 [39m[48;5;65m - **Docstrings**: Google style with Args/Returns sections[49m
     [38;5;246m17 [39m[48;5;65m - **Error Handling**: Use try/except with specific exceptions and logging[49m
     [38;5;246m18 [39m[48;5;65m - **Naming**: [49m
     [38;5;246m19 [39m[48;5;65m   - Classes: CamelCase[49m
     [38;5;246m20 [39m[48;5;65m   - Functions/variables: snake_case[49m
     [38;5;246m21 [39m[48;5;65m   - Private methods: _prefixed[49m
     [38;5;246m22 [39m[48;5;65m - **Architecture**: Modular with clear separation of concerns[49m
     [38;5;246m23 [39m
     [38;5;246m24 [39m[48;5;95m 2. **Database Layer**[49m
     [38;5;246m25 [39m[48;5;95m    - Supabase for persistent storage[49m
     [38;5;246m26 [39m[48;5;95m    - Tables for artifish, bluesky_accounts, humans, post_references, post_content, etc.[49m
     [38;5;246m27 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memory system for storing persistent information about users and interactions[49m
     [38;5;246m28 [39m[48;5;95m [49m
     [38;5;246m29 [39m[48;5;95m 3. **Memory System**[49m
     [38;5;246m30 [39m[48;5;95m    - Memgraph for graph-based memory and relationship modeling[49m
     [38;5;246m31 [39m[48;5;95m    - Emojikeys for sentiment analysis[49m
     [38;5;246m32 [39m[48;5;95m    - Interest tracking for understanding users' preferences[49m
     [38;5;246m33 [39m[48;5;95m [49m
     [38;5;246m34 [39m[48;5;95m 4. **Network Crawler**[49m
     [38;5;246m35 [39m[48;5;95m    - Utility to explore and map the Bluesky social graph[49m
     [38;5;246m36 [39m[48;5;95m    - Collects relationships and interest data for agents[49m
     [38;5;246m37 [39m[48;5;95m [49m
     [38;5;246m38 [39m[48;5;95m ## Key Libraries[49m
     [38;5;246m39 [39m[48;5;95m - Google ADK (Agent Development Kit) for agent orchestration[49m
     [38;5;246m40 [39m[48;5;95m - Supabase Python client for database operations[49m
     [38;5;246m41 [39m[48;5;95m - Neo4j/Memgraph libraries (neo4j, gqlalchemy) for graph operations[49m
     [38;5;246m42 [39m[48;5;95m - Bluesky Python client for network interactions[49m
     [38;5;246m43 [39m[48;5;95m [49m
     [38;5;246m44 [39m[48;5;95m ## Important Notes[49m
     [38;5;246m45 [39m[48;5;95m - The project is in initial development[49m
     [38;5;246m46 [39m[48;5;95m - We're using UV for package management[49m
     [38;5;246m47 [39m[48;5;95m - dot-env for environment configuration[49m
     [38;5;246m48 [39m[48;5;95m - We prefer a minimal, clean approach to architecture[49m
     [38;5;246m24 [39m[48;5;65m ## Project Structure[49m
     [38;5;246m25 [39m[48;5;65m Artifish is a suite of AI agents for Bluesky built with Google ADK, using Supabase for storage and Memgraph [49m
     for relationship modeling. Core components include: Agent System, Database Layer, Memory System, and Network
     Crawler.
     [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;65mfor relationship modeling. Core components include: Agent System, Database Layer, Memory System, and Network [49m
     [38;5;246m   [39m[48;5;65mCrawler.[49m
     [38;5;246m26 [39m\ No newline at end of file
